TITLE: Creating and Adding Custom Format Checker (Go)
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates how to create a custom format checker for role validation and add it to gojsonschema. This allows for custom string format validation in JSON schemas.
SOURCE: https://github.com/kubesphere/kubesphere/blob/master/vendor/github.com/open-policy-agent/opa/internal/gojsonschema/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_19

LANGUAGE: go
CODE:
```
// Define the format checker
type RoleFormatChecker struct {}

// Ensure it meets the gojsonschema.FormatChecker interface
func (f RoleFormatChecker) IsFormat(input interface{}) bool {

    asString, ok := input.(string)
    if ok == false {
        return false
    }

    return strings.HasPrefix("ROLE_", asString)
}

// Add it to the library
gojsonschema.FormatCheckers.Add("role", RoleFormatChecker{})
```

