TITLE: Custom TOML Unmarshaling with TextUnmarshaler
DESCRIPTION: Advanced example showing how to implement custom unmarshaling for email addresses using the TextUnmarshaler interface
SOURCE: https://github.com/kubesphere/kubesphere/blob/master/vendor/github.com/BurntSushi/toml/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: toml
CODE:
