TITLE: Testing Logrus Output with the Test Hook
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use Logrus's built-in testing facilities to assert the presence of log messages in tests, using the test hook and a null logger.
SOURCE: https://github.com/kubesphere/kubesphere/blob/master/vendor/github.com/sirupsen/logrus/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: go
