TITLE: Defining Starlark Expressions in EBNF
DESCRIPTION: Grammar rules for expressions in Starlark, including test, lambda, if-expressions, and primary expressions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/kubesphere/kubesphere/blob/master/vendor/go.starlark.net/syntax/grammar.txt#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: EBNF
CODE:
```
Test = LambdaExpr
     | IfExpr
     | PrimaryExpr
     | UnaryExpr
     | BinaryExpr
     .

LambdaExpr = 'lambda' [Parameters] ':' Test .

IfExpr = Test 'if' Test 'else' Test .

PrimaryExpr = Operand
            | PrimaryExpr DotSuffix
            | PrimaryExpr CallSuffix
            | PrimaryExpr SliceSuffix
            .

Operand = identifier
        | int | float | string
        | ListExpr | ListComp
        | DictExpr | DictComp
        | '(' [Expression [',']] ')'
        | ('-' | '+') PrimaryExpr
        .
```

